The holidays are pretty boring most of the time but who wants to go back to skool next week?! Not me~!
neways i have nothing to do in the second week but for the first week this is what really happened:

Monday~
went out with Zin and Els to Burwood to look around. Didn't really do much, then we went back to Zin's place and our pathetic attempt at table tennis was hopeless...^_______^" i hit the lamp 5 or 6 times...^___^"

Thursday~
went with Tomo to Kinokuniya and she bought manga and NewType. The book i wanted was out of stock 0>_<0 damn~! after we took sticker photos and the little punk tried to choke me~! =P then we went back to her place

Friday~
went to Elsa's house to try to teach her how to use photoshop but her sis was online so didn't get the chance...and it was raining cats that day -.-" we were all wet...

Saturday~
went to Campsie with my parents and got my ears pierced again! this time just one more on the right side...hope it doesn't infect or nething...

well that's pretty much it and Animania is coming up! well guess i can't wait...
and Nina, never call me at 9 something again!
